-- HSBC and BNP to finance Iliad's US mobile bid - sources
-- 
-- Fri Aug 01, 2014 03:32AM EDT
-- None



PARIS, Aug 1 (Reuters) - French telecoms company Iliad <ILD.PA> has lined up financing for its $15 billion bid for 56.6 percent of T-Mobile US <TMUS.N> from BNP Paribas <BNPP.PA> and HSBC <HSBA.L>, three people familiar with the matter said on Friday.

